OL,3,CThe 96-year-old multi-millionaire
OL,4,Cliving in hotel for two years
OL,6,FA 96-year-old multi-millionaire living
OL,7,Fin a Jersey hotel for the last two
OL,8,Fyears says he would not want to be
OL,9,Fanywhere else.
OL,11,FIn 2022, Stuart Weaving and his wife
OL,12,FDorothy wanted to downsize to live a
OL,13,Fmore relaxing life.
OL,15,FHe now has a large room at The Grand
OL,16,FHotel with a view overlooking St
OL,17,FAubin's Bay.
OL,19,FStuart told ITV News: "There are a lot
OL,20,Fof wonderful homes in Jersey, but
OL,21,Fthey're not as good as this.
