OL,3,CThe 96-year-old multi-millionaire
OL,4,Cliving in hotel for two years
OL,6,FSpeaking about what attracted him and
OL,7,FDorothy to The Grand, he said: "I
OL,8,Fdon't have the energy I used to have,
OL,9,Fsometimes I'd like a little nod off or
OL,10,Fsomething like that.
OL,12,F"Staying in a hotel like this, we can
OL,13,Fjust go into the bedroom and nod off,
OL,14,Fgo to sleep, for a few hours then it
OL,15,Fdoesn't take up much of our life, it
OL,16,Fjust refreshes us and we're on again."
