OL,3,CThe 96-year-old multi-millionaire
OL,4,Cliving in hotel for two years
OL,6,FHe added: "Dorothy was finding it
OL,7,Fquite difficult to run a home, buying
OL,8,Ffood and cooking and this sort of
OL,9,Fthing and just cleaning and making the
OL,10,Fbeds.
OL,12,F"I didn't want to do more washing up
OL,13,Fand things like that and so we decided
OL,14,Fto let somebody else do it.
OL,16,F"We come down to meals and it's laid
OL,17,Fout there ready for us, on our own
OL,18,Ftable there and the staff are just
OL,19,Flike family to us."
